trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref:System.DateTime> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representa um <xref:System.DateTime>propriedade (e o respetivo valor) de um componente de hardware ou software de sistema impressão.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> classe para a propriedade especificada.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.DateTime> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente o mesmo que o nome de algumas determinado <xref:System.DateTime>propriedade de um objeto de sistema de impressão, incluindo as maiúsculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "StartTimeOfDay", not "StartTime" or "Starttimeofday".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objeto tem de ser escrito "StartTimeOfDay", não "StartTime" ou "Starttimeofday".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.DateTime> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref:System.DateTime>propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> representa.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> classe que tem o valor especificado para o atributo especificado.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.DateTime> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente o mesmo que o nome de algumas determinado <xref:System.DateTime>propriedade de um objeto de sistema de impressão, incluindo as maiúsculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "StartTimeOfDay", not "StartTime" or "Starttimeofday".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objeto tem de ser escrito "StartTimeOfDay", não "StartTime" ou "Starttimeofday".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.StartTimeOfDay%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.DateTime> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref:System.DateTime>propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> representa.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> representa.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor da propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintDateTimeProperty"> </xref> representa.
